sentences: Kip Christian Moore (born April 2, 1980) is an American country music singer and songwriter signed to MCA Nashville.
He has released a total of four studio albums for the label: Up All Night, Wild Ones, Slowheart, and Wild World.

Moore then released "I'm to Blame", the lead single to his 2015 album, Wild Ones.
Slowheart (2017–2018)
